document.topic_text: Mahuta family eyes up more Waikato seats Monday, 22 August 2016 ( 37 minutes ago ) Nanaia Mahuta's husband is the latest family member to put his hat in the ring for the upcoming elections - wanting to be on the governance board of the council he once worked for.The Hauraki-Waikato Labour party MP's younger sister...
